<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Welcome to ACCMaR@MUST on Advanced Computations for Chemistry and Materials Research (ACCMaR)</title><link>https://ACCMaR-Group.github.io/group-website/</link><description>Recent content in Welcome to ACCMaR@MUST on Advanced Computations for Chemistry and Materials Research (ACCMaR)</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 17 Jan 2026 02:10:00 -0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://ACCMaR-Group.github.io/group-website/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>ACCMaR is Recruiting!</title><link>https://ACCMaR-Group.github.io/group-website/news/recruiting/</link><pubDate>Sat, 17 Jan 2026 02:10:00 -0800</pubDate><guid>https://ACCMaR-Group.github.io/group-website/news/recruiting/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;We are currently recruiting researchers of the following categories.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="1-postdocs"&gt;1. Postdocs&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Two Postdoc positions are available in ACCMaR, with one working in Macau SAR and the other working at the Innovation and Technology Research Institute in Hengqin. The PI will offer competitive salary and benefits in accordance with university and local regulations, along with a supportive, respectful, and international working environment.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="msg msg--info"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Attention:&lt;/b&gt; Postdoc candidates that are interested in working in Hengqin might be eligible for receiving extra stipend and research fund from the talent program of the municipal government. See&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://www.hengqin.gov.cn/macao_zh_hans/zwgk/zcfg/zyzc/index.html"&gt;https://www.hengqin.gov.cn/macao_zh_hans/zwgk/zcfg/zyzc/index.html&lt;/a&gt; for further details.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Dr. Weng joined MUST</title><link>https://ACCMaR-Group.github.io/group-website/news/joined-must/</link><pubDate>Mon, 12 Jan 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ACCMaR-Group.github.io/group-website/news/joined-must/</guid><description>&lt;div class="gallery-wrapper"&gt;
