&lt;p&gt;12/01/2026: Dr. Weng officially joined Macau University of Science and Technology as an Assistant
 Professor and independent PI. He founded his research group named ACCMaR from scratch. He will
 conduct research at both the LIU's Innovation and Technology Center in Macau SAR, and the Innovation
 Technology Research Center in Hengqin. His teaching activities will happen on the main campus of
 MUST.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>1st NC-FBM&amp;ECMST in Nanjing</title><link>https://ACCMaR-Group.github.io/group-website/news/conference/</link><pubDate>Mon, 05 Jan 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ACCMaR-Group.github.io/group-website/news/conference/</guid><description>&lt;div class="gallery-wrapper"&gt;
